OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FThis means that the energy bill for
OL,8,Fthe average household paying by direct
OL,9,Fdebit for gas and electricity will
OL,10,Frise from the current #1,720 to #1,755
OL,11,Fper year.
OL,13,FUswitch calculated that the average
OL,14,Fhome on a standard tariff would spend
OL,15,F#140 on energy in October compared
OL,16,Fwith #63 in September, thanks to a
OL,17,Fcombination of higher rates and
OL,18,Fincreased usage in autumn.
