OL,5,Crise
OL,7,FAround 2.7 million more low-income
OL,8,Fhouseholds, including 900,000 families
OL,9,Fwith children, are eligible for the
OL,10,F#150 Warm Home Discount this winter,
OL,11,Fafter the Government confirmed it
OL,12,Fwould remove the "hard to heat"
OL,13,Feligibility criteria.
OL,15,FThe Government has said the change
OL,16,Fwill see an estimated 6.1 million
OL,17,Fhouseholds receive the discount this
OL,18,Fwinter.
