OL,7,FOfgem said the latest increase was
OL,8,Falso driven by an increase in
OL,9,Felectricity balancing costs ` incurred
OL,10,Fby network operators to ensure a
OL,11,Fstable electricity supply for when
OL,12,Fthere is both too much power and too
OL,13,Flittle power in the system ` adding
OL,14,Faround #1.23 a month to the average
OL,15,Fhousehold bill.
