OL,7,FThe End Fuel Poverty Coalition said
OL,8,Fthe latest increase represented a
OL,9,F2.21% year-on-year rise and meant
OL,10,Fenergy bills would be 68% or #713 a
OL,11,Fyear higher than in the winter of 2020-
OL,12,F21.
OL,14,FOfgem changes the price cap for
OL,15,Fhouseholds every three months, largely
OL,16,Fbased on the cost of energy on
OL,17,Fwholesale markets.
